column1: Subject: Building, Real Estate, Construction and Housing
Table Title: Available And Vacant Executive Condominiums And Supply Of Executive Condominiums In The Pipeline By Development Status (End Of Period), Quarterly

Refers to completed executive condominium units that are available for physical occupation, including both occupied and unoccupied units.  Data include all completed executive condominiums issued with a temporary occupation permit, or a certificate of statutory completion.
Refers to available executive condominiums that are not physically occupied.
Total Supply By Development Status (Number Of Units):
Comprises supply of uncompleted executive condominiums in approved or planned projects which are under construction as well as those on which construction has not started yet.
Total Supply By Development Status -> Under Construction (Number Of Units):
Projects are deem to be under construction when a permit to commence building works in respect of that building is issued by the Commissioner of Building Control.
Total Supply By Development Status -> Planned - Others (Number Of Units):

Comprises supply of uncompleted executive condominiums for which applications have been submitted to URA but are under consideration, projects on awarded Government Land Sales (GLS) sites for which plans have not been submitted for planning approval, and planned projects in the Government Land Sales programme (which refers to sites on the GLS confirmed list and sites on the GLS reserve list that have been triggered).  Construction of this group of projects has not commenced yet.
na   not available or not applicable
-     nil or negligible or not significant
Numbers may not add up to the totals due to rounding.
Data are the latest available at the time of access or download. Some statistics, particularly those for the most recent time periods, are provisional and may be subject to revision at a later date.
Values are shown in Singapore dollars (unless otherwise specified).
